.IX Header "ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES"
None. In future versions \f(CW$NICELOAD\fR will be able to contain default settings.
.SH "EXIT STATUS"
.IX Header "EXIT STATUS"
Exit status should be the same as the command being run (untested).
